OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,FMore than three-quarters of people who
OL,7,Fuse cannabis in Guernsey have admitted
OL,8,Fit was not prescribed to them
OL,9,Fdirectly, according to a new report.
OL,11,FWhile a 2025 report shows about 11.9%
OL,12,Fof those living in Guernsey and
OL,13,FAlderney over the age of 16 have
OL,14,Freportedly used cannabis in a 12-month
OL,15,Fperiod, 78.8% of those did not have it
OL,16,Fprescribed to them.
OL,18,FIt raises concerns that most people
OL,19,Fusing cannabis are using it in a
OL,20,Fstrong medicinal grade.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
