CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey publishes its
OL,7,FCombined Substance Use Strategy 2027-
OL,8,F2032, setting out the Bailiwick's next
OL,9,Ffive-year plan to reduce the harms
OL,10,Fassociated with alcohol, drugs, and
OL,11,Fnicotine products.
OL,13,FWith the increase in people using
OL,14,Fcannabis, health authorities are now
OL,15,Fwarning islanders of the dangers of
OL,16,Fdrug misuse and want to review the
OL,17,Fprescription process.
OL,19,FCannabis is still a Class B drug, and
OL,20,Ftaking it recreationally is still a
OL,21,Fcriminal offence.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,FPeople who are using someone else's
OL,7,Fmedicinal cannabis also run the same
OL,8,Frisks attached to any prescribed drug,
OL,9,Fwhich could put anyone taking it
OL,10,Fwithout medical supervision in danger
OL,11,Fof several side effects.
OL,13,FStakeholders of the 2025 report agreed
OL,14,Fthat while drug use among the
OL,15,FBailiwick's young people was low,
OL,16,Fservices felt they lacked
OL,17,Funderstanding about why taking someone
OL,18,Felse's prescribed cannabis was illegal.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,F"The concern around the diversion of
OL,7,Fmedicinal cannabis is using a
OL,8,Fmedicinal product in an unsupervised
OL,9,Fway," Dr Nicola Brink, Guernsey's
OL,10,FDirector of Public Health, told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,F"The normalisation of cannabis use is
OL,14,Fa significant concern. The Strategy
OL,15,Fincludes actions to strengthen
OL,16,Fregulation of prescribing clinics and
OL,17,Fto develop reporting mechanisms for
OL,18,Fconcerns regarding prescribing
OL,19,Fpractices and illicit diversion."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,FThe Combined Substance Use Strategy
OL,7,Fforms part of the 2025 Joint Strategic
OL,8,FNeeds Assessment (JSNA) - a
OL,9,Fcomprehensive overview of substance
OL,10,Fuse across the islands.
OL,12,FIt outlines strategies to deal with
OL,13,Fcannabis, alongside other substances
OL,14,Fthat can be harmful to islanders.
OL,16,FRecommendations include a review of
OL,17,Fmedicinal cannabis prescribing, with a
OL,18,Ffocus on regulation of prescribing
OL,19,Fclinics and the development of
OL,20,Fstandardised reporting for
OL,21,Finappropriate prescribing.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,FThe JSNA also recommends creating an
OL,7,Fearly-warning drug system to identify
OL,8,Fnew trends in drug use across the
OL,9,FBailiwick.
OL,11,FIt specifically highlights taking a
OL,12,Fproactive approach to the growing
OL,13,Fpresence of substances such as CBD
OL,14,Fproducts, synthetic opioids, and high-
OL,15,Fcaffeine energy drinks.
OL,17,FJSNA stakeholders also suggest looking
OL,18,Fat better supporting islanders' basic
OL,19,Fneeds - such as secure housing - can
OL,20,Fhelp to reduce or stop an individual's
OL,21,Fsubstance abuse.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774033868
OL,3,C78% of Guernsey cannabis users use
OL,4,Csomeone else's prescription, data finds
OL,6,FAmy Sharpe, a Public Health
OL,7,FPractitioner, told ITV News: "We heard
OL,8,Flots of concerns surrounding
OL,9,Fnormalisation of use around young
OL,10,Fpeople and also the illicit diversion.
OL,12,F"A piece of work is going on with the
OL,13,FChief Pharmacist to look at the
OL,14,Fregulation of cannabis, and we're
OL,15,Fpleased that this data, as part of the
OL,16,FJoint Strategic Needs Assessment, can
OL,17,Fhelp to inform this."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
